❌ XSS 테스트: 없음
```

### 예시 필요 테스트
```typescript
// T5-1: SQL Injection
test('prevent SQL injection', () => {
  const malicious = "'; DROP TABLE users; --";
  const result = stdlib.sanitize(malicious);
  expect(result).not.toContain("DROP");
});

// T5-2: ReDoS
test('prevent ReDoS attack', () => {
  const regex = /^(a+)+$/;
  const malicious = 'a'.repeat(50);
  expect(() => {
    stdlib.test(malicious, regex);
  }).not.toThrow();
});
```

